- ca sa aflu hostname: hostnamectl 

- 3 tipuri de hostname:
	- static: Assigned by the system admin
	- dinamic: Assigned by DHCP or mDNS server at runtime
	- pretty: Assigned by the system admin. Its can be used as Description like “Oracle DB server”
	
Cum se seteaza hostname:	
hostnamectl set-hostname numeserver    ## static
hostnamectl set-hostname "Nume Server"   ## pretty

relogin ca sa vezi ca a mers, restart ca sa fii sigur ca merge

alternative:
- nmcli
- nmtui
editez /etc/hostname (restart)
